 Config Skill\n\nModify Claude Code configuration by updating settings.json files.\n\n## When Hooks Are Required (Not Memory)\n\nIf the user wants something to happen automatically in response to an EVENT, they need a **hook** configured in settings.json. Memory/preferences cannot trigger automated actions.\n\n**These require hooks:**\n- \"Before compacting, ask me what to preserve\" ‚Üí PreCompact ho‚Ä¶","sessionId":"15ea2d14-712c-4e18-aada-4b11145ef4eb","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:23:21.659Z","title":"prompt_submit","type":"conversation"},"obs_mqwtkgxd_55c3526277bd":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgxd_55c3526277bd","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"15ea2d14-712c-4e18-aada-4b11145ef4eb","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:23:27.791Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgxd_eb580ce25436":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgxd_eb580ce25436","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"echo \\\"=== settings.json ===\\\" && cat /Users/gwang/Develop/noteboard/.claude/settings.json; echo \\\"=== skills dir ===\\\"; ls -R /Users/gwang/Develop/noteboard/.claude/skills/ 2>/dev/null; echo \\\"=== commands dir ===\\\"; ls -R /Users/gwang/Develop/noteboard/.claude/commands/ 2>/dev/null; echo \\\"=== grep Security-guidance ===\\\"; grep -ri \\\"security-guidance\\\" /Users/gwang/Develop/noteboar‚Ä¶","sessionId":"15ea2d14-712c-4e18-aada-4b11145ef4eb","subtitle":"{\"command\":\"echo \\\"=== settings.json ===\\\" && cat /Users/gwang/Develop/noteboard/.claude/settings.json; echo \\\"=== skil‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:23:30.045Z","title":"Bash","type":"command_run"},"obs_mqwtkgxd_32e2e2c6a56b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgxd_32e2e2c6a56b","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_0136a6U5t6sw7rZrKoQ5P2rG\"} | === settings.json ===\n{\n  \"enabledPlugins\": {\n    \"superpowers@claude-plugins-official\": true,\n    \"last30days@last30days-skill\": true,\n   